e-Less-Skincare-1682436331984512/"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.agelessskinandlasers.com/reviews/page/28/"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.portraitcare.com/location/age-less-skincare-13012/"},{"type":"url","url":"https://agelessmedspakaty.com/"},{"type":"url","url":"https://reviews.birdeye.com/ageless-med-spa-145376287029425"}]}},{"id":"tco_0d159da7-f462-985a-adc3-646ff0a7212d_call-e730dffa-7611-458a-8cc3-e4e43c74222f-3","summary":[],"type":"reasoning","status":"completed"},{"id":"tco_0d159da7-f462-985a-adc3-646ff0a7212d_call-e730dffa-7611-458a-8cc3-e4e43c74222f-4","summary":[],"type":"reasoning","status":"completed"},{"id":"tco_0d159da7-f462-985a-adc3-646ff0a7212d_call-e730dffa-7611-458a-8cc3-e4e43c74222f-5","summary":[],"type":"reasoning","status":"completed"},{"content":[{"type":"output_text","text":"**Top-rated options for chemical peel facials in Katy, TX, based on recent Yelp reviews and local listings (as of 2026 data), include highly reviewed estheticians and medspas specializing in customized peels for issues like acne, aging, hyperpigmentation, and uneven texture.**[[1]](https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Chemical+Peel&find_loc=Katy%2C+TX)[[1]](https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Chemical+Peel&find_loc=Katy%2C+TX)\n\n### Highest-Rated from Yelp Searches\n- **Age Less Skincare** (5.0 stars from 34+ reviews): Praised for knowledgeable, gentle estheticians (e.g., Candice) who tailor treatments, explain processes, and deliver noticeable skin improvements. Ideal for personalized facials and peels in a non-corporate setting.[[2]](https://www.yelp.com/biz/age-less-skincare-katy)\n- **Facials by Jada** (4.8 stars from 30+ reviews): Clients highlight skilled, calming sessions with excellent results for skin clarity, glow, and issues like acne scars. Often mentioned for chemical peels and dermaplaning combos.[[3]](https://www.yelp.com/biz/facials-by-jada-katy)\n- **Face to Face Spa** (4.9 stars from 35+ reviews): Strong feedback on clean facilities, friendly service, and effective customized chemical peels for brighter, smoother skin.[[4]](https://www.yelp.com/biz/face-to-face-spa-katy-11)\n\nOther notable mentions include Divinity Spa and places like Cinco Ranch Dermatology for more clinical options.[[1]](https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Chemical+Peel&find_loc=Katy%2C+TX)\n\n### Medical/Clinical Providers\nFor stronger or medically supervised peels (e.g., VI peels, TCA, or those addressing deeper concerns):\n- **Clear Dermatology**, **AVIVA Dermatology**, **Viata Aesthetics**, **Glow Up MD Spa**, **Katy Medi Spa**, and **Anita's Skin Care Clinic** offer chemical peels alongside facials, often with dermatologist oversight or advanced options like those targeting acne scars or aging.[[5]](https://cleardermatology.com/our-services/skincare-treatments-and-aesthetic/chemical-peels-facials/)[[6]](https://www.avivaderm.com/chemical-peel-dermatologist-katy-tx/)[[7]](https://www.viataaestheticsandwellness.com/chemical-peels/)\n- **Hibiscus Health** and **Face to Face Spa** (Cinco Ranch location) emphasize resurfacing for healthier skin.[[8]](https://www.hibiscus.health/facial-treatments/chemical-peels/)[[9]](https://facetofacespa.com/cinco-ranch/chemical-peels/)\n\n### Tips for Choosing\n- **Yelp and review sites** consistently rank the above esthetician-focused spots highest for \"chemical peel\" searches in Katy—check recent photos/reviews for before-and-afters.[[1]](https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Chemical+Peel&find_loc=Katy%2C+TX)\n- Consider your skin type/goals: Estheticians like those at Age Less or Facials by Jada excel at milder, facial-style peels; dermatology/medspas (e.g., AVIVA or Clear) suit deeper treatments.\n- Always schedule a consultation to discuss peel strength (e.g., glycolic, salicylic, VI), downtime, and suitability. Results vary; multiple sessions are often recommended.\n- Verify current licensing, specials, and availability directly, as offerings change.\n\nSearch Yelp for \"Chemical Peel Katy TX\" or contact providers for the latest details and to confirm they match your needs.[[1]](https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Chemical+Peel&find_loc=Katy%2C+TX)","logprobs":[],"annotations":[{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Chemical+Peel&find_loc=Katy%2C+TX","start_index":277,"end_index":355,"title":"1"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Chemical+Peel&find_loc=Katy%2C+TX","start_index":355,"end_index":433,"title":"1"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.yelp.com/biz/age-less-skincare-katy","start_index":741,"end_index":795,"title":"2"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.yelp.com/biz/facials-by-jada-katy","start_index":1026,"end_index":1078,"title":"3"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.yelp.com/biz/face-to-face-spa-katy-11","start_index":1255,"end_index":1311,"title":"4"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Chemical+Peel&find_loc=Katy%2C+TX","start_index":1423,"end_index":1501,"title":"1"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://cleardermatology.com/our-services/skincare-treatments-and-aesthetic/chemical-peels-facials/","start_index":1915,"end_index":2021,"title":"5"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.avivaderm.com/chemical-peel-dermatologist-katy-tx/","start_index":2021,"end_index":2090,"title":"6"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.viataaestheticsandwellness.com/chemical-peels/","start_index":2090,"end_index":2155,"title":"7"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.hibiscus.health/facial-treatments/chemical-peels/","start_index":2267,"end_index":2335,"title":"8"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://facetofacespa.com/cinco-ranch/chemical-peels/","start_index":2335,"end_index":2395,"title":"9"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Chemical+Peel&find_loc=Katy%2C+TX","start_index":2596,"end_index":2674,"title":"1"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Chemi